<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Projet RP Avocat — Dossier de Présentation</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@400;700;900&family=Cormorant+Garant:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,500&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { background: #0a0905; color: #f5f0e8; font-family: 'Cormorant Garant', serif; overflow-x: hidden; }

/* TYPO */
.fc { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; }
.fm { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
.fco { font-family: 'Cormorant Garant', serif; }

/* COLORS */
.gold { color: #c9a84c; }
.cream { color: #f5f0e8; }
.muted { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); }

/* NAV */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  padding: 18px 60px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  transition: all 0.4s;
}
nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(10,9,5,0.96);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
}
.nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.nav-logo-text { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #f5f0e8; font-weight: 700; }
.nav-badge { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #0a0905; background: #c9a84c; padding: 3px 10px; }
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; }
.nav-links a { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
.nav-links a:hover { color: #c9a84c; }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: #0a0905;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.1) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 70%, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 0%, transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 70%, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 0%, transparent 45%);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  padding: 120px 40px 80px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M30 0 L31 29 L60 30 L31 31 L30 60 L29 31 L0 30 L29 29 Z' fill='none' stroke='rgba(201,168,76,0.03)' stroke-width='0.5'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size: 60px 60px; pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-tag { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #0a0905; background: #c9a84c; padding: 6px 20px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.hero-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 72px); font-weight: 700; color: #f5f0e8; letter-spacing: 4px; line-height: 1.1; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.hero-sub { font-family: 'Cormorant Garant', serif; font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 26px); color: #c9a84c; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 3px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.hero-desc { font-family: 'Cormorant Garant', serif; font-size: 19px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.9; max-width: 640px; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto 52px; font-style: italic; }
.hero-pills { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 56px; }
.pill { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c9a84c; padding: 7px 18px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.35); }
.pill.filled { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08); }

/* DIVIDER */
.div { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.div .dl { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(201,168,76,0.35)); }
.div .dr { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.35), transparent); }
.div .dd { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #c9a84c; transform: rotate(45deg); flex-shrink: 0; }
.div .ds { width: 3px; height: 3px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.4); transform: rotate(45deg); flex-shrink: 0; }
.div-center { justify-content: center; max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* SECTION */
section { padding: 110px 60px; }
.section-label { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c9a84c; display: block; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.section-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 36px); color: #f5f0e8; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 18px; }

/* FRAMED */
.framed { position: relative; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); }
.framed .c { position: absolute; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5); border-style: solid; }
.framed .c-tl { top: 0; left: 0; border-width: 1px 0 0 1px; }
.framed .c-tr { top: 0; right: 0; border-width: 1px 1px 0 0; }
.framed .c-bl { bottom: 0; left: 0; border-width: 0 0 1px 1px; }
.framed .c-br { bottom: 0; right: 0; border-width: 0 1px 1px 0; }

/* REVEAL */
.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease; }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* MARQUEE */
.marquee-band { background: #c9a84c; padding: 16px 0; overflow: hidden; }
.marquee-inner { display: flex; animation: marquee 40s linear infinite; white-space: nowrap; width: max-content; }
.marquee-inner span { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #0a0905; margin-right: 72px; }
@keyframes marquee { from { transform: translateX(0); } to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

/* ===== VISION ===== */
.vision-grid { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start; }
.vision-text p { font-size: 19px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.62); line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 22px; }
.vision-text p strong { color: #c9a84c; font-weight: 500; }
.impact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
.impact-card { background: #111009; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding: 22px 20px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: border-color 0.3s; }
.impact-card:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.4); }
.impact-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent, #c9a84c), transparent); transform: scaleX(0); transition: transform 0.4s; }
.impact-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
.impact-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.impact-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 11px; color: #f5f0e8; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.impact-desc { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }
.impact-card.police { --accent: #4a7fc1; border-color: rgba(74,127,193,0.2); }
.impact-card.gang { --accent: #c14a4a; border-color: rgba(193,74,74,0.2); }
.impact-card.press { --accent: #4ac18a; border-color: rgba(74,193,138,0.2); }
.impact-card.civil { --accent: #c9a84c; }

/* ===== STRUCTURE ===== */
.ranks-wrap { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
.rank-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr auto;
  gap: 0; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
  margin-bottom: 2px; background: #111009;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  align-items: stretch;
}
.rank-row:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.35); background: #13120a; }
.rank-badge-col { padding: 24px 28px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
.rank-tier { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.rank-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #f5f0e8; }
.rank-body { padding: 24px 28px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
.rank-desc { font-size: 17px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.6); line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.rank-tasks { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
.rank-tag { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); color: rgba(201,168,76,0.7); }
.rank-num-col { padding: 24px 28px; border-left: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-width: 80px; }
.rank-num { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 28px; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.15); font-weight: 700; }

.rank-row.senior .rank-tier { color: #c9a84c; }
.rank-row.senior { border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c; }
.rank-row.intermediaire .rank-tier { color: #a0bcd4; }
.rank-row.intermediaire { border-left: 3px solid #4a7fc1; }
.rank-row.junior .rank-tier { color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5); }
.rank-row.junior { border-left: 3px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3); }
.rank-row.commis .rank-tier { color: #4ac18a; }
.rank-row.commis { border-left: 3px solid #4ac18a; }

/* ===== REMUNERATION ===== */
.remu-grid { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
.remu-card { background: #111009; padding: 44px 36px; position: relative; transition: background 0.3s; }
.remu-card:hover { background: #13120a; }
.remu-num { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 52px; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.07); position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 20px; line-height: 1; }
.remu-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.remu-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 13px; color: #f5f0e8; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.remu-desc { font-size: 17px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 22px; }
.remu-example { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05); border-left: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3); padding: 14px 16px; font-size: 15px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.6; }
.remu-example strong { color: #c9a84c; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; }

/* ===== FILES ===== */
.files-grid { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
.file-card { background: #111009; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding: 36px; display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; transition: border-color 0.3s; }
.file-card:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.4); }
.file-icon-wrap { width: 52px; height: 52px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.04); }
.file-content { flex: 1; }
.file-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 12px; color: #f5f0e8; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.file-desc { font-size: 16px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.file-tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.file-tag { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c9a84c; padding: 3px 9px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25); }
.file-status { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #4ac18a; padding: 3px 9px; border: 1px solid rgba(74,193,138,0.3); background: rgba(74,193,138,0.06); }

/* ===== PROCESS ===== */
.process-wrap { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
.process-step { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 0; position: relative; }
.process-step:not(:last-child)::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 39px; top: 80px; bottom: -2px; width: 1px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.4), rgba(201,168,76,0.05)); z-index: 0; }
.step-num-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding-top: 28px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.step-circle { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.5); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #0a0905; font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 14px; color: #c9a84c; }
.step-body { padding: 20px 0 40px 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08); margin-bottom: 2px; }
.process-step:last-child .step-body { border-bottom: none; }
.step-label { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.6); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.step-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 15px; color: #f5f0e8; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.step-desc { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.58); line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; }
.step-roles { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 12px; }
.step-role { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 12px; }
.step-role.police { color: #4a7fc1; border: 1px solid rgba(74,127,193,0.35); background: rgba(74,127,193,0.06); }
.step-role.gang { color: #c14a4a; border: 1px solid rgba(193,74,74,0.35); background: rgba(193,74,74,0.06); }
.step-role.avocat { color: #c9a84c; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.35); background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06); }
.step-role.presse { color: #4ac18a; border: 1px solid rgba(74,193,138,0.35); background: rgba(74,193,138,0.06); }
.step-role.civil { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.15); }

/* ===== STATS BAND ===== */
.stats-band { background: #111009; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12); padding: 60px; }
.stats-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
.stat-item { background: #111009; padding: 40px 28px; text-align: center; }
.stat-num { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 36px; color: #c9a84c; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.stat-label { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.35); }

/* ===== CTA ===== */
.cta-section { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0905, #0d0c08); padding: 110px 60px; text-align: center; }
.cta-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
.cta-section .section-title { font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 40px); margin-bottom: 24px; }
.cta-section p { font-size: 19px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.btn-gold { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #0a0905; background: #c9a84c; padding: 16px 44px; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.3s; display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-gold:hover { background: #e8c97a; }
.btn-outline { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c9a84c; background: transparent; padding: 15px 44px; border: 1px solid #c9a84c; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08); }
.cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

/* FOOTER */
footer { background: #060504; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1); padding: 44px 60px; }
.footer-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; }
.footer-left span { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #f5f0e8; }
.footer-left p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garant', serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.25); font-style: italic; margin-top: 4px; }
.footer-right { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 9px; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.18); letter-spacing: 2px; }

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:900px){
  nav { padding: 16px 20px; }
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  section { padding: 72px 20px; }
  .vision-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .remu-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .files-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
  .rank-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .rank-num-col { display: none; }
  .rank-badge-col { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  .impact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <span style="color:#c9a84c;font-size:16px">⚖</span>
    <span class="nav-logo-text">HAMPTON <span style="color:#c9a84c">&</span> CO.</span>
    <span class="nav-badge">Dossier Admin</span>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#vision">Vision</a>
    <a href="#structure">Structure</a>
    <a href="#remuneration">Rémunération</a>
    <a href="#fichiers">Fichiers RP</a>
    <a href="#processus">Processus</a>
    <a href="#localisation">Localisation</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div style="text-align:center;max-width:900px;position:relative;z-index:2;">
    <span class="hero-tag">Dossier de Présentation · Administration Serveur</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title">PROJET RP AVOCAT</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Hampton & Co. — Cabinet Juridique</p>
    <div class="div div-center" style="margin-bottom:36px"><div class="dl"></div><div class="ds"></div><div class="dd"></div><div class="ds"></div><div class="dr"></div></div>
    <p class="hero-desc">Une proposition sérieuse pour enrichir l'écosystème juridique du serveur avec un RP avocat structuré, documenté et interconnecté avec la police, les gangs et la presse.</p>
    <div class="hero-pills">
      <span class="pill filled">RP Sérieux</span>
      <span class="pill">Hiérarchie structurée</span>
      <span class="pill">Documents prêts</span>
      <span class="pill filled">Commis d'office</span>
      <span class="pill">Multi-factions</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="#vision" class="btn-gold">Découvrir le projet</a>
      <a href="#fichiers" class="btn-outline">Voir les fichiers</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="position:absolute;bottom:36px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);opacity:0.3;text-align:center;">
    <div style="width:1px;height:40px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,#c9a84c);margin:0 auto"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MARQUEE -->
<div class="marquee-band">
  <div class="marquee-inner" id="marquee"></div>
</div>

<!-- VISION -->
<section id="vision" style="background:#0d0c08;">
  <div class="vision-grid">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="section-label">Vision du Projet</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Un RP Juridique Complet & Sérieux</h2>
      <div class="div" style="margin-bottom:28px"><div class="dl"></div><div class="ds"></div><div class="dd"></div><div class="ds"></div><div class="dr"></div></div>
      <div class="vision-text">
        <p>Le RP avocat est l'un des <strong>maillons manquants</strong> de nombreux serveurs. Sans défense juridique crédible, les arrestations et procès restent superficiels, privant policiers, criminels et civils d'une dimension narrative puissante.</p>
        <p>Hampton & Co. propose un cadre <strong>rigoureux et documenté</strong> pour installer un véritable système judiciaire en jeu : des avocats hiérarchisés, des procédures établies, des documents modèles prêts à l'emploi pour les nouveaux joueurs.</p>
        <p>Ce n'est pas un simple rôle de figurant. C'est un <strong>pilier de l'écosystème RP</strong> qui génère de l'interaction pour toutes les factions du serveur.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
      <span class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:20px;display:block">Impact sur les Factions</span>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card police">
